description:
Got rid of those annoying sonar tracks that was ruining this tab. Its not like this site is a challenge to perfectly recreate the song via midi, its to learn tabs while being able to also hear them. If you want to make midi music, thats fine. I have nothing against that, I enjoy making beep tunes for my computers beeper speaker, who am I to judge. Just do it on....not a tab site.....Especially if you're just going to shrug off a crappy background effect that doesn't need to be there in the first place and it being there makes the track unlistenable....Like....seriously....
(via editor)
